GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/tags/invalid-id-format
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}


### Test: Tag Not Found
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/tags/507f1f77bcf86cd799439011
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}


### Test: Create Tag Without Name
# Should return 400 Bad Request
POST {{apiBaseUrl}}/tags
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "description": "Test tag"
}


### Test: Create Duplicate Tag
# Should return 400 if tag with same slug exists
POST {{apiBaseUrl}}/tags
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Existing Tag Name",
  "slug": "existing-slug"
}


### Test: Merge Tag Into Itself
# Should return 400 Bad Request
POST {{apiBaseUrl}}/tags/merge
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "sourceTagId": "{{testTagId}}",
  "targetTagId": "{{testTagId}}"
}


### Test: Bulk Tag with Empty Array
POST {{apiBaseUrl}}/tags/{{testTagId}}/bulk-tag
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "ingredientIds": []
}


### Test: Get Tag by Invalid Slug
GET {{apiBaseUrl}}/tags/slug/non-existent-slug
Authorization: Bearer {{bearerToken}}


### Test: Unauthorized Access
